[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0201","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0201.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0085","title":"IBM AIX rwhod 远程缓冲区溢出代码执行漏洞","description":"AIX 及其他类 Unix 操作系统中的 rwhod 服务存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向目标系统发送包含超长主机名的特制 UDP 数据包触发该漏洞，导致任意代码执行。该漏洞影响 AIX、FreeBSD 等多款操作系统，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。该漏洞属于经典的远程缓冲区溢出问题，攻击者只需构造恶意 UDP 报文即可远程利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0085"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1996-08-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:32.770","remediation":"立即禁用 rwhod 服务（命令：`killall rwhod` 并注释 /etc/inetd.conf 中 rwhod 行），若确需使用 rwhod，请升级 AIX 至 4.3.3 以上或 FreeBSD 至 3.2 以上版本。同时在防火墙上阻止外部对 UDP 端口 513 的访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/118","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/119"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0201.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0282","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0282.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0132","title":"HP HP-UX Expreserve 任意文件写入漏洞","description":"HP-UX 系统中 vi 和 ex 编辑器调用的 expreserve 工具未对文件路径进行充分校验，存在任意文件写入漏洞。本地攻击者可利用编辑器暂存文件机制，将缓存内容写入系统任意文件，覆盖关键配置文件或可执行程序，从而获得 root 权限。该漏洞攻击复杂度低，但需本地访问权限。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0132"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1996-08-15T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:39.687","remediation":"立即安装 HP 当时发布的安全补丁（HP-UX Security Patch 针对 vi/expreserve 组件）。如无法安装补丁，可临时移除 Expreserve 程序的 setuid 位：执行 chmod u-s /usr/lib/expreserve（或系统对应路径），以消除本地用户利用该漏洞进行提权的攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-1996-19.html","http://www.osvdb.org/11723","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/401"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0282.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0283","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0283.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0133","title":"Adobe Framemaker fm_fls License Server 任意文件写入漏洞","description":"Adobe Framemaker 的 fm_fls 许可证服务器存在任意文件写入漏洞，本地攻击者可利用该服务覆盖系统中任意文件，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞允许具有本地访问权限的用户通过发送特制请求修改关键系统文件，导致权限提升。CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低，攻击前提是拥有本地系统访问权限。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0133"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1996-08-14T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:39.843","remediation":"升级 Adobe Framemaker 至厂商修复版本；若无法升级，立即移除 fm_fls 二进制文件的 setuid root 权限（chmod u-s /path/to/fm_fls），并严格限制可执行该二进制文件的用户组，仅授权给需要管理许可的信任用户。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0133"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0283.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0284","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0284.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0134","title":"Sun Solaris vold 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Solaris 2.x 系统中的卷管理守护进程 vold 存在权限漏洞，本地普通用户可利用该缺陷获取 root 超级用户权限。攻击者通过向 vold 发送特制请求或利用其在处理卷管理操作时权限检查不足的漏洞，实现本地权限提升。该漏洞影响 Solaris 2.x 系列操作系统，需拥有系统本地账户方可利用，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0134"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1996-08-06T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:40.020","remediation":"安装 Sun 针对 Solaris 2.x 的 vold 安全补丁（Solaris 2.4 对应补丁 101945，Solaris 2.5/2.5.1 对应补丁 103600），升级至已修复版本。如无法立即打补丁，可停止 vold 服务（/etc/init.d/volmgt stop）并禁用自动启动，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/8159"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0284.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1268","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1268.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1413","title":"Sun Microsystems Solaris Coredump 文件写入漏洞","description":"Solaris 2.4 至 7.0 版本内核存在 set-gid 程序核心转储权限检查缺陷，当真实用户 ID 不属于 set-gid 组时，系统仍允许 set-gid 程序生成 core dump 文件。本地攻击者可利用 dmesg 等方式触发 set-gid 程序崩溃，通过控制 core dump 文件名和路径覆盖或创建高权限文件，从而提升至更高权限。该漏洞需要本地访问权限，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1413"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1996-08-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:23.280","remediation":"升级 Solaris 2.4 内核至安装 jumbo patch -35 或更高版本（如 Solaris 2.5 及以上已修复）。如无法立即打补丁，可临时限制普通用户对 set-gid 程序的执行权限，并通过脚本定期清理 /core 等核心转储目录，避免低权限用户利用 core dump 越权覆盖或创建文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167419549&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/296","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19236","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/8057fa2fdc38632692a6b3f836dd95e1eb8504fd/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1413.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1413","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/15e59d23a2add4a8eeec666e251338b2844c0e85/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1413.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1413.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f61040ac78eb76aff0a3a68a8a8a4562940d3711/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6v6p-c65q-8x22/GHSA-6v6p-c65q-8x22.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/9ef5a1e2753195eb4be450895da310f7a8a6524e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1413.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154500_154600.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000093.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/296/info.html","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--ac4ce242-c926-4c44-8a08-c1709e4c4139.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1268.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0551","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0551.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0335","title":"多款 Unix 系统 lpr 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"该漏洞为 BSD 系系统中 lpr 命令处理 -C（classification）命令行选项时的缓冲区溢出漏洞。lpr 程序未对用户输入的 -C 参数长度进行充分校验，本地攻击者可构造超长字符串作为 -C 参数传入，触发栈缓冲区溢出，从而以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 BSD/OS 2.1、FreeBSD 2.1.5、NeXTstep 4.x、IRIX 6.4、SunOS 4.1.3/4.1.4 及基于 BSD 的 Linux 系统，CVSS v2 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0335"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1996-08-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:57.050","remediation":"DUPLICATE: CVE-1999-0335 is a duplicate of CVE-1999-0032. Refer to CVE-1999-0032 for the canonical vulnerability entry. No AVE entry generated.","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19544","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/af5cedcf472f3690d94c4249ff35246f15692534/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0335.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0335","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/ec31d5593e31331ed2058e001803e087d65aa416/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0335.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5jj5-vh28-7x64/GHSA-5jj5-vh28-7x64.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0335.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_0.list.dict","https://github.com/shamedgh/confine/blob/a75dad3ad336e6258a42cd1ce4af061eea68ed76/cve.files/cveToFile.json.type.csv","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000092.txt","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0551.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0287","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0287.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0136","title":"Sun Microsystems Solaris KCMS 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Solaris 系统中 Kodak 色彩管理系统（KCMS）存在权限提升漏洞。本地攻击者利用 KCMS 组件对文件操作权限校验不严的缺陷，可向任意系统文件写入恶意数据，从而获得 root 权限。该漏洞影响 Sun Solaris 操作系统，攻击者需拥有本地账户作为前置条件，无需其他认证。成功利用后可完全控制目标系统。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0136"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1996-07-31T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:40.370","remediation":"安装 Sun 官方补丁（Solaris 2.5 对应补丁 ID 103093-01，Solaris 2.5.1 对应补丁 ID 103094-01）以修复 KCMS 组件权限问题；如无法打补丁，可临时移除 KCMS 相关 setuid 二进制文件（如 /usr/dt/bin/kcms_calibrate）的 setuid 位以阻止本地提权。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0136"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0287.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0286","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0286.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0135","title":"Sun Solaris admintool 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Solaris admintool 存在基于符号链接的任意文件写入漏洞。本地用户可通过在 /tmp 目录下创建恶意符号链接，诱使以 root 权限运行的 admintool 向系统任意位置写入数据，进而覆盖 /etc/passwd 等关键文件实现权限提升。该漏洞影响 Solaris 2.3 至 2.6 版本，攻击者需具备本地用户账户，利用条件简单，危害严重。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0135"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1996-07-25T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:40.207","remediation":"立即安装 Solaris 厂商安全补丁（如 Sun Patch 106874），升级到未受影响的 Solaris 版本；临时缓解措施可移除 admintool 的 setuid 权限（chmod 4755 /usr/bin/admintool）或通过 group 限制仅允许受信任管理员执行该工具。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0135"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0286.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0077","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0077.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0023","title":"多个Unix系统厂商 rdist 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"rdist 工具的 lookup() 函数存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地用户通过向该函数传递特制参数触发缓冲区溢出，从而覆盖内存数据并获得 root 权限。该漏洞影响 BSDI BSD/OS 2.1、FreeBSD 2.1、IBM AIX 4.2、SGI IRIX 6.4、Sun SunOS 4.1.3 等多个 UNIX 系统。攻击者需拥有本地账号并具备调用 rdist 的权限，无需网络远程利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0023"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1996-07-24T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:22.417","remediation":"升级 FreeBSD 至 2.1.5 或更高版本；SunOS 4.1.3 安装补丁 102079-05，Solaris 安装补丁 103600；AIX 升级至 4.2.1 或安装 APAR IX67810；IRIX 安装 SGI 补丁 1695 或升级至 6.5；BSDi 升级至 BSD/OS 2.1.1。如无法立即升级，可移除 rdist 的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /usr/bin/rdist）并改用 rsync 替代。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0023","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19106"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0077.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0075","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0075.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0023","title":"多款Unix系统 rdist 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"rdist 远程文件分发工具的 lookup() 函数存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可利用特制输入触发栈缓冲区溢出，覆盖返回地址或函数指针，从而以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 BSDI BSD/OS 2.1、FreeBSD 2.1、IBM AIX 4.2、SGI IRIX 6.4、Sun SunOS 4.1.3 等多个 Unix 系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。攻击者需拥有本地账户并执行恶意构造的 rdist 命令即可提权至 root。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0023"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1996-07-24T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:22.417","remediation":"立即升级 rdist 至安全版本（如 FreeBSD 2.2.1 及以上、SunOS 5.5.1 及以上），禁用 rdist 的 setuid 位 (`chmod u-s /usr/bin/rdist`)，并在非必要环境下彻底移除 rdist 服务端或改用 rsync 替代。对仍运行 AIX 4.2/IRIX 6.4 等已停止支持的系统，建议迁移至现代操作系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0023","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19106","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0023.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0023","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0023.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0023.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0023.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-p5x8-wgxf-7w54/GHSA-p5x8-wgxf-7w54.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0023.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154500_154600.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--2250a918-956c-42c3-8640-fd1457b43a36.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0075.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1464","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1464.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1301","title":"FreeBSD rzsz 组件 Z-Modem 协议远程代码执行漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 2.1.5 之前版本中的 rzsz 模块所实现的 Z-Modem 协议存在设计缺陷，远程攻击者可通过向客户端发送特制文件，在 rz 程序处理过程中利用协议命令注入执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 FreeBSD 操作系统，危害等级高，可能导致目标系统被完全控制。需升级至 FreeBSD 2.1.5 或更高版本以修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1301"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1996-07-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:08.943","remediation":"升级 FreeBSD 至 2.1.5 或更高版本，该版本已修复 rz/rzsz 模块中 Z-Modem 协议的设计缺陷。如无法升级，建议禁用 rz/sz 命令的 setuid 权限，并限制仅受信来源可发起文件传输。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/g-31.shtml","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7540.php","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/24df5d59670dfe04b9c86de11fa86df63c0d28f7/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1301.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1301","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1301.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/228df6a85079f5c6b1ecdfb3d41be685458438ef/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1301.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/4544d3857250fe21711ce8febf38e8822729678f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-57xw-6c7g-xh67/GHSA-57xw-6c7g-xh67.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154500_154600.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1301.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000089.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--7a0517f4-bfeb-4736-973e-112eedebb156.json","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1464.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0288","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0288.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0137","title":"Linux dip 本地缓冲区溢出提权漏洞","description":"Linux 系统中 dip（Dial-up IP）程序 3.3.7 版本存在本地缓冲区溢出漏洞。由于 dip 程序在处理用户输入时未正确校验缓冲区边界，本地攻击者可利用该漏洞向 dip 程序发送精心构造的超长参数触发栈溢出，覆盖返回地址，从而以 root 权限执行任意代码，实现本地权限提升。该漏洞 CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高，攻击者需拥有系统本地访问权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0137"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1996-07-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:40.520","remediation":"升级 dip 至 3.7.3 或更高版本以修复缓冲区溢出问题。如无法升级，立即执行 `chmod u-s /usr/sbin/dip` 移除 dip 二进制文件的 setuid 权限位作为临时缓解。现代 Linux 发行版已不再包含 dip，建议彻底卸载 dip 软件包并改用 pppd 替代 SLIP/PPP 拨号功能。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0137","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19078","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0137.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0137","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0137.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0137.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0137.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6hwp-66fm-v8h9/GHSA-6hwp-66fm-v8h9.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0137.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_0.list.dict","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/86/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0288.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0071","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0071.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0022","title":"FreeBSD rdist 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"CVE-1999-0022 是 FreeBSD 系统中 rdist 远程文件分发工具的 expstr() 函数存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。由于该函数未对输入长度进行有效边界检查，本地攻击者可构造特制数据触发缓冲区越界读取，从而将权限提升至 root。该漏洞影响多个 FreeBSD 版本，攻击者需具备本地系统账户权限才能利用，CVSS 评分 7.8，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0022"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1996-07-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:22.167","remediation":"升级 FreeBSD 至 6.4-RELEASE 或更高版本（rdist 自 FreeBSD 7.0 起已从 base 系统移除，建议直接移除 rdist 或移除其 setuid 位：`chmod u-s /usr/bin/rdist`）。如无法升级，卸载 rdist 软件包或通过 `chflags schg /usr/bin/rdist` 防止篡改利用。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/179"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0071.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0349","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0349.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0175","title":"Novell NetWare Web Server 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Novell NetWare Web Server 2.x 的 convert.bas 程序存在未授权文件读取漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，通过发送特制的 HTTP 请求即可利用该脚本读取 Web 服务器内部可访问的任意文件。该漏洞可能泄露系统配置文件、密码文件及敏感业务数据，进而为后续攻击提供信息支撑。CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0175"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1996-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:45.673","remediation":"立即删除或重命名 Web 服务端 scripts 目录下的 convert.bas 文件以消除文件读取风险；升级至 Novell NetWare 5.1 或更高版本（该版本改用基于 Netscape 的企业级 Web 服务器，不再包含 convert.bas）；如仍在运行已停止支持的 NetWare 平台，应尽快迁移至 SUSE Linux Enterprise Server 或 Windows Server 等现代操作系统。临时缓解措施可在防火墙或 Web 服务器配置中限制对 scripts 目录的访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0175","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20448","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea60fdb4a03411be38d3e381b26e4c4/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0175.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0175","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0175.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0175.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0175.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-g2vw-843m-4hr9/GHSA-g2vw-843m-4hr9.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/web-misc.rules","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0175.json","https://github.com/magicsword-io/Magic-SigExplorer/blob/2c28b91b003429a144a687199ee99ebd26f1a343/Magic-SigExplorer/docs/cve_report.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0349.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0289","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0289.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0138","title":"Perl suidperl 权限提升漏洞","description":"suidperl 和 sperl 程序在处理 setuid 脚本时存在权限提升漏洞。当切换 UID 回原始用户时，这两个程序未能正确释放 root 权限，导致本地普通用户可利用此缺陷获取超级用户权限。攻击者通过精心构造的 setuid Perl 脚本触发此漏洞，实现本地权限提升。该漏洞影响早期多个 UNIX 系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0138"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1996-06-26T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:40.677","remediation":"升级 Perl 至 5.004 或更高版本，该版本修复了 suidperl 在切换回原始用户 UID 时未正确丢弃 root 权限的问题。如无法立即升级，执行 chmod u-s /usr/bin/suidperl /usr/bin/sperl 移除 suid 特权位作为临时缓解措施；同时建议使用 sudo 替代 suidperl 机制，或使用 C 包装程序调用 Perl 脚本来避免内核竞态条件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0138"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0289.toml"}]